Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:01.64,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry, the place is a bit of a mess, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.46,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,I haven't cleaned up or...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:06.65,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,...or showered since you were last here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:10.53,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,But it's not just me, you know. I've added another roommate to the mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:14.24,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,You all remember Fawkes, the Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:16.54,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Dumbledore left him to me when he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:22.30,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Fawkes is a great roommate, keeps to himself, sleeps in the fireplace,...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:26.35,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Unlike that sleepy dragon over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.58,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,WAKE UP, YOU BASTARD!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:30.05,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:33.64,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Woah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:35.64,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.25,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Harry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:40.57,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Where's that glowing smile of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:43.66,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Wait. You're acting like something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:45.31,Harry,,0,0,0,,Something IS wrong, Hagrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:47.31,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:49.46,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,I tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:54.20,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,You come right over here and sit on old Hagrid's lap, best seat in the house! \N[Reference to starship by team starkid]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:55.78,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.25,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.40,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Now here's a warning:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:03.15,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna bounce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:03.92,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:07.86,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,That feels good, doesn't it? Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:13.90,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that feels good. If you have to spit up just do it right into Hagrid's beard. That's what I always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:16.34,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Now tell me what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:20.00,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Harry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:22.43,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[:-DDD]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.62,Harry,,0,0,0,,Oh... it's NOTHING, Hagrid! \N[Massively breaking the fourth wall ;-P]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:42.78,Harry,,0,0,0,,Well, life just sucks, that's all, okay? It's like people don't even care that I'm Harry Potter anymore. Neville doesn't even stutter around me anymore, he's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:47.40,Harry,,0,0,0,,...he's acting less like he's got a schlong-bottom, and more like he's got a big old shlonky dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:57.39,Harry,,0,0,0,,I've saved the world like a million times. How can everybody just forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:00.59,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Harry, don't you f***ing talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:06.28,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,You might be wee, but you got a greatness in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:09.63,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Whether you're flying around on that little broom of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:11.80,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,or singing a song or two,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:16.60,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,or maybe reminding us all, that we're not alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:22.52,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Like... for some people, Harry, you are the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:29.23,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,At the end of a very dark, lonely, shameful tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:30.86,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,You're a hero, Harry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:36.26,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,As timeless and unforgetable as the VR Troopers.\N[VR=virtual reality]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:38.68,Ron,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:40.68,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,The VR Troopers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:45.25,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,What, you never heard of this? They're like three little kids superheroes with this mechanical suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.25,Harry,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean like Beetleborgs \N[the in-official follow up to this series]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:48.09,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Beetleborgs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:49.71,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:53.45,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Beetleborgs are shit! I'm talking about... ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:56.54,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,The VR Troopers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:08:02.78,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,They were cool! They had this amazing ability to travel through the power-lines... or the inter net, or... you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:07.28,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,... ah, I actually can't clear remember what they did, but my point is:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:10.69,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,You're like them, cherished for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:16.16,Harry,,0,0,0,,But Hagrid, all my life I've only been known as the savior of Hogwarts, so what does it mean when I'm not at Hogwarts anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:16.93,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Uhum...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:19.07,Harry,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.90,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:22.49,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Harry,...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:25.58,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,I was once in the same position as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:31.66,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,A senior, pacing down the inevitable end of school and childhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.35,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,And I didn't want to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:35.84,Harry,,0,0,0,,So what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.84,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,I didn't let it go, I never left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:40.46,Harry,,0,0,0,,You never left Hogwarts?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:41.12,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:45.86,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Oh, they wanted me to leave. But I refused to attend graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:47.86,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,I'm tecnically still a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:51.37,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,But when you love something
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:53.37,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,so much
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:57.01,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,And you see it slipping through your fingers, Harry
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:09:00.70,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,You just got to hold on tighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:01.96,Harry,,0,0,0,,You're hurting me, Hagrid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:03.07,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Oh! Harry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:07.82,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,My advice to you is: nevery change!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:10.16,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,It's fun living at Hogwarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:15.55,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Sure, all your friends'll grow up and start families of their own,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:18.49,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,but eventually their kids will come to Hogwarts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.04,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,And you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.82,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,It'll... it'll be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.54,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,So sad to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:31.57,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,You'll probably just sit down in your hut most days, watching NetFlix or Hulu Plus,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:38.85,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,waiting for... three rosy cheeked little angles to come down for a visit
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:42.34,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,maybe ask for a dance-lesson or advice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:46.05,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Soon they'll grow up too, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.68,0:09:49.22,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,...they won't come around as much anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:50.91,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,And you'll wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:52.91,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,...why you keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:55.60,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Before you know it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:57.37,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,...your only company...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:10:01.77,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,... is a dragon that's been asleep for five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:04.74,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,...and a Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:08.88,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,That's just to remind you how short life is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:15.14,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,But we don't get second chances like that Phoenix, do we, kids? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:20.25,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Once we've burned, we're toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:26.00,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,Well, pep talk's over! Thanks for coming down to cheer me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.00,Ron,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Hagrid! This has been fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.37,Hermione,,0,0,0,,We'd better get back to the dorms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:31.17,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,But wait, you don't have to go yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:32.60,Ron,,0,0,0,,Haha! Bye, Hagrid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:34.00,Hagrid,,0,0,0,,I... if you...*sigh*
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:36.85,Ron,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hagrid always has the best advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:42.62,Ron,,0,0,0,,Well, Harry, we didn't quite find the Chamber of Secrets monster, but do you at least feel a little bit better?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:47.11,Harry,,0,0,0,,No. Like hardly no, not at all, I feel terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
